IMPORTANT NOTICE - RESPONSIBLE USE

This software is designed for legitimate personal and professional use. Users
must comply with all applicable laws and regulations regarding keyboard
monitoring and data privacy.

PROHIBITED USES:
- Unauthorized monitoring of third parties
- Employee surveillance without proper consent and disclosure
- Any use that violates privacy laws or regulations
- Circumventing security measures
- Malicious or deceptive purposes

LEGAL COMPLIANCE:
Always obtain proper consent before monitoring keyboard activity. Ensure
compliance with local, state, and federal laws including but not limited to:
- GDPR (Europe)
- CCPA (California)
- Wiretapping and surveillance laws
- Employment and labor laws

The authors and contributors are not responsible for misuse of this software.
